// Real, minimal document fixtures whose text is extracted by Apache Tika via the
// loader's native extractor. PDF only: the PDF below was generated by PDFBox and
// verified to round-trip through Tika's PDF parser, so `buildDocument` returns an
// `ai:TextDocument` whose content contains the marker text. This loader does not
// support Microsoft Office formats (they are skipped like binaries), so no Office
// fixtures are kept here.

// A valid PDF (PDFBox) whose only text is `PDF_TEXT`.
final readonly & byte[] PDF_BYTES = base64 ``;

// The marker text Tika extracts from the PDF fixture above.
const string PDF_TEXT = "Mock PDF document text.";
